<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>Acclamation to the Gospel During Lent</B></FONT></H2>
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">According to the Liturgical year (A-B-C) and according to the week (from 1st to 5th)
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">use the acclamation from the Missal with one of the following melodies:</FONT>
